The least squares regression equations for β0 and β1 are:
β1 = (nΣ(XY) - ΣX ΣY) / (nΣX^2 - (ΣX)^2)
β0 = (ΣY - β1ΣX) / n

ΣX^2 = (13^2) + (14^2) + (-8^2) + (3^2) + (7^2) = 317
